00:26:28,758 --> 00:26:31,707
55, 55. 60.

340
00:26:31,747 --> 00:26:33,811
60,60…成交！
60, 60- sold!

341
00:26:33,825 --> 00:26:37,283
40. 40, 40, 45.

342
00:26:37,329 --> 00:26:40,924
45, 45, 45. 50.

343
00:26:40,966 --> 00:26:44,333
50. 50, 50. 55.

344
00:26:44,854 --> 00:26:49,073
这是一个好市场，但都是些骨瘦如材的
This is bona stock, but it's all skin and bone, eh?

345
00:26:49,113 --> 00:26:51,043
你想想要个好价钱
You want a good price.

346
00:26:51,113 --> 00:26:54,262
让我们给他们食物吃，给他们增点肥
Let us feed them up, put some fat on them.

347
00:26:54,322 --> 00:26:58,351
只需要几周的小康生活，这些奴隶就会卖得和鹅心一样好
Couple weeks of easy living, and these puppies will sell like duck hearts.

348
00:26:58,381 --> 00:27:00,351
买食物以及储存食物会很贵吗？
Is that expensive, fodder and storage?

349
00:27:00,391 --> 00:27:04,010
不！你会赚回你花在食物上的钱的两倍
No! You'll recoup feed and storage double.

350
00:27:10,578 --> 00:27:13,328
漂亮，对吧？一个真实的表演者
Beautiful, neh? A real showman.

351
00:27:13,358 --> 00:27:16,097
我虽然不是万能的
I am no judge of the sand,

352
00:27:16,157 --> 00:27:18,836
但肯定每个人都能看到
but sure, anyone can see

353
00:27:18,876 --> 00:27:23,765
他是稀有的强壮，充满攻击性
he is rare large and aggressive.

354
00:27:25,685 --> 00:27:28,524
当明天的元老院会议召开
When the Senate meets tomorrow,

355
00:27:28,564 --> 00:27:32,283
西比乌会提议一项对凯撒的终结方案
Scipio will propose an ultimatum be put to Caesar.

356
00:27:32,323 --> 00:27:35,642
我以朋友的身份，希望你明天支持这项方案
I ask you as a friend to support the proposal

357
00:27:35,692 --> 00:27:38,072
并吩咐你的朋友们都来支持
and to enjoin your many friends to do the same.

358
00:27:38,112 --> 00:27:41,331
哦，我并没有多少朋友
Oh, I have not so many friends as all that.

359
00:27:41,371 --> 00:27:44,040
啊，温和派像绵羊一样跟随你
Ah, the moderates follow you like sheep.

360
00:27:44,080 --> 00:27:46,630
你的选票非常关键，最终方案是？
 Your vote is critical.  The ultimatum is?

361
00:27:46,670 --> 00:27:48,999
凯撒的任职期一结束
Caesar's term of office is over.

362
00:27:49,039 --> 00:27:51,209
他必须马上解散他的军队
He must immediately disband his men,

363
00:27:51,239 --> 00:27:53,938
辞去他的指挥权，并回来接受审判…
resign his command, and return for trial--

364
00:27:53,968 --> 00:27:57,997
不然的话，他就被当作是元老院和人民的敌人
else be considered an Enemy of the Senate and People of Rome.

365
00:27:58,027 --> 00:28:00,526
但他不会接受的
But he cannot accept that.

366
00:28:00,556 --> 00:28:01,906
那让他身败名裂
Not without dishonor.

367
00:28:01,936 --> 00:28:05,755
一但宣布敌对，他便没有什么可以失去的了…他便会不顾一切的战斗
Once declared hostile, he has nothing to lose- he will fight at any cost.

368
00:28:05,795 --> 00:28:07,385
他会宣布战争！
You are declaring war!

369
00:28:07,425 --> 00:28:11,104
轮不到凯撒决定
Caesar will not have to accept or refuse the terms,

370
00:28:11,134 --> 00:28:15,083
马克·安东尼会直接否决
because Mark Antony will immediately use Tribune's veto.

371
00:28:15,113 --> 00:28:16,483
你的意图是？
But then, what is your purpose?

372
00:28:16,523 --> 00:28:18,452
如果议会反对他
If the Senate votes against him,

373
00:28:18,492 --> 00:28:20,952
恺撒会明白
Caesar will finally understand

374
00:28:20,992 --> 00:28:24,011
他只有孤身一人
that he is alone against all.

375
00:28:24,051 --> 00:28:26,400
除了一张否决票
Of course, anything but an overwhelming vote

376
00:28:26,450 --> 00:28:30,030
让恺撒觉得还有希望
encourages Caesar to think he still has friends and hope.

377
00:28:35,698 --> 00:28:38,518
我不是恺撒的朋友
I am no friend to Caesar, nor any tyrant,

378
00:28:38,548 --> 00:28:40,377
谈我不会否决提议
but I cannot vote for a proposal

379
00:28:40,417 --> 00:28:44,066
那样太没有信仰了
I do not wish to see realized. It would be highly irreligious.

380
00:28:44,106 --> 00:28:46,016
我向朱庇特宣过誓
I have made a vow to Jupiter.

381
00:28:46,046 --> 00:28:49,165
除非明天我能获得全部议员的支持
Unless I get the full backing of the Senate tomorrow,

382
00:28:49,205 --> 00:28:52,284
否则我就把我全部的军团带去西班牙
I and all my legions will sail for Spain

383
00:28:52,324 --> 00:28:56,463
让你们这帮绅士自生自灭
and leave you gentlemen to your own defenses.

384
00:29:06,241 --> 00:29:08,501
这就是他？
This is he? Crito?

385
00:29:08,551 --> 00:29:10,600
他是个好孩子
He's a good boy from good family.

386
00:29:10,630 --> 00:29:13,099
好到让大爷我的
Good enough to seed a child of the vorenii

387
00:29:13,169 --> 00:29:15,179
女儿怀孕？
who fought at Magnesia and Zama?

388
00:29:15,209 --> 00:29:17,878
我不知道，先生 你不知道？！
 I don't rightly know, sir.  You don't rightly know?!

389
00:29:17,908 --> 00:29:20,218
你不知道她是我的？
Do you know that this girl is my property?

390
00:29:20,248 --> 00:29:21,937
应该先征得我的同意
That you should have asked my permission

391
00:29:21,977 --> 00:29:23,587
在你们乱搞之前？
before you coupled with her?

392
00:29:23,627 --> 00:29:27,746
对不起  我现在就有杀你的权利
 I'm sorry, sir.  I am within my rights to kill you here and now.

393
00:29:27,786 --> 00:29:30,445
爸爸，别，别现在才这样
 Papa, please.  Don't you start sniffling.

394
00:29:30,485 --> 00:29:32,485
你被搞之前应该先想到这些
You should have thought of this before you spread your legs.

395
00:29:32,515 --> 00:29:34,854
他们没有要侮辱你
They meant you no disrespect.

396
00:29:34,924 --> 00:29:36,084
他们做的很正常
What they did was only natural.

397
00:29:36,124 --> 00:29:37,964
他们年轻，又相爱着对方
They're young and they love each other.

398
00:29:37,994 --> 00:29:39,453
还是不可容忍
That's no excuse.

399
00:29:39,503 --> 00:29:42,183
他妈妈家里很有钱
His mother's family are well-found in Ostia for many generations,

400
00:29:42,233 --> 00:29:45,482
他爸爸又是很成功的商人
and his father is a successful drover.

401
00:29:46,482 --> 00:29:48,481
他们家就在街对面
They have a house in the southern crossroads.

402
00:29:48,761 --> 00:29:50,591
房间里肯定都是牛粪
A house built from cattle dung no doubt.

403
00:29:50,621 --> 00:29:53,560
那里很干净，一点味道都没有
It's very hygienic, sir. There's no smell.

404
00:29:53,792 --> 00:29:55,760
Huh!

405
00:29:55,779 --> 00:29:58,169
至少家畜商还有钱赚
There's money in droving, at least.

406
00:29:58,199 --> 00:29:59,729
很多钱
Good money, sir.

407
00:29:59,769 --> 00:30:02,118
对于我来说…
I'm on the Capua run mostly--

408
00:30:02,148 --> 00:30:05,637
一星期至少5,000
that's 5,000 head a week sometimes, sir.

409
00:30:06,327 --> 00:30:08,946
不可思议，你什么时候成人？
He cannot be but what he is. When are you a man?

410
00:30:08,976 --> 00:30:12,256
下个月，先生 下个月
 Next month, sir.  Next month.

411
00:30:15,395 --> 00:30:17,844
很好，下个月你和我女儿成婚
very well, you may marry my daughter.

412
00:30:17,884 --> 00:30:22,573
和你家人讲准备好嫁妆
Assure your good people that the dowry will be appropriate.

413
00:30:31,451 --> 00:30:33,170
他是个好孩子
He really is a good boy.

414
00:30:33,264 --> 00:30:36,131
你应该感到高兴
You should be pleased.

415
00:30:36,210 --> 00:30:39,699
我女儿失去童贞
My daughter's virginity has been taken

416
00:30:39,959 --> 00:30:43,918
我第一个孙子居然是穷人的孩子
and my first grandson spawned, by an ill-favored prole.

417
00:30:43,978 --> 00:30:45,828
我怎么能高兴？
How can I be pleased?

418
00:30:45,888 --> 00:30:47,657
 他让她开心  她真是个傻瓜
 He makes her happy.  She's an idiot then.

419
00:30:47,687 --> 00:30:49,987
你真残忍！
What a brute you are!

420
00:31:25,968 --> 00:31:31,337
议员们，听马赛琉斯说
The Senate will hear Metullus Scipio.

421
00:31:31,347 --> 00:31:33,417
说吧！
Speak! Speak!

422
00:31:33,467 --> 00:31:38,315
议员们，我提议
Conscript fathers, I propose a formal motion.

423
00:31:38,345 --> 00:31:41,755
除非盖乌斯·优利乌斯·恺撒
Unless Gaius Julius Caesar

424
00:31:41,795 --> 00:31:44,874
立刻放弃他的指挥权
immediately lays down his command,

425
00:31:44,914 --> 00:31:49,163
解散他的军队然后回罗马
disbands his legions and returns to Rome for trial,

426
00:31:49,223 --> 00:31:53,582
否则议会将宣布他是个公敌
this sacred assembly will declare him a public enemy

427
00:31:53,622 --> 00:31:56,341
罗马人民的敌人！
of the Senate and People of Rome!

428
00:31:56,381 --> 00:32:00,140
在那之后
After which time it will be the duty

429
00:32:00,190 --> 00:32:04,169
那将是所有罗马人的义务
and the obligation of every Roman to do him harm

430
00:32:04,199 --> 00:32:07,709
去杀掉他！
or to kill him if they are able!

431
00:32:16,167 --> 00:32:19,226
议案已经提出了
A motion is proposed.

432
00:32:19,256 --> 00:32:22,855
同意的请表态
Those in favor, make it known.

433
00:32:55,407 --> 00:33:01,206
议案通过
The motion is carried by clear numbers.

434
00:33:02,746 --> 00:33:04,425
安东尼！
Antony!

435
00:33:04,515 --> 00:33:06,825
否决它！
veto the motion!

436
00:33:06,925 --> 00:33:10,554
快否决！
Stand up! veto the motion!

437
00:33:11,903 --> 00:33:16,162
大家安静！大家注意！
I demand the floor! I demand the floor!

438
00:33:16,202 --> 00:33:18,822
听他说！ 我否议案！
 Give him the floor!  I veto the motion!

439
00:33:18,882 --> 00:33:21,751
护民管否决议案！
Tribune vetoes the motion!

440
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:26,650
西比乌的议案反对凯撒
Scipio's motion against Caesar--

441
00:33:26,700 --> 00:33:28,969
立不住脚，对吗？
it doesn't stand, does it?

442
00:33:29,029 --> 00:33:30,579
立的住脚
Stands.

443
00:33:30,639 --> 00:33:33,198
记入年报
Entered in the annals.

444
00:33:33,278 --> 00:33:37,417
护民官反对也不行？
Despite that Tribune raised his veto?

445
00:33:37,437 --> 00:33:42,026
反对没有成立
Not heard, not fully admitted.

446
00:33:42,206 --> 00:33:43,956
分量不够
No weight.

447
00:33:44,006 --> 00:33:46,775
议案通过
The motion stands.

448
00:33:46,855 --> 00:33:48,925
我跟你讲清楚
Let me be clear with you.

449
00:33:48,985 --> 00:33:50,594
我不希望
I do not wish

450
00:33:50,644 --> 00:33:52,514
这样重要的议案
that a motion as important as this

451
00:33:52,554 --> 00:33:55,493
用这种诡计通过
should stand on a mere trick of procedure.

452
00:33:55,543 --> 00:33:57,623
你说诡计？
Trick, you say?

453
00:33:57,663 --> 00:34:00,162
这是宗教的方式
This is a religious matter.

454
00:34:00,232 --> 00:34:03,711
宗教里容不得诡计
There are no tricks in religion.

455
00:34:05,201 --> 00:34:09,300
会议还没正式结束，对吗？
Session was not formally ended, correct?

456
00:34:10,970 --> 00:34:13,929
对，当复会后
 Correct.  So, when we reconvene,

457
00:34:13,989 --> 00:34:17,218
还是一样
it will formally be the same session.

458
00:34:18,189 --> 00:34:21,454
护民官安东尼可以否决
Then Tribune Antony may use veto on the motion.

459
00:34:28,256 --> 00:34:30,685
是的
That is so.

460
00:34:30,865 --> 00:34:34,594
天后朱庇特！ 老笨蛋
Juno lnferna! Senile old fool,

461
00:34:34,634 --> 00:34:36,544
为什么你一开始不说？
why didn't you say so to begin with?

462
00:34:36,594 --> 00:34:40,753
马克·安东尼不可以收到任何伤害
Mark Antony must not be harmed or hindered in any way.

463
00:34:40,903 --> 00:34:41,512
但是…无论如何
 But-  In any way!

464
00:34:41,512 --> 00:34:45,292
让他能否决这个提议，这一点很重要
It is vitally important that he be allowed to veto the motion.

465
00:34:45,750 --> 00:34:48,418
否则，凯撒就成叛国者了
If he does not, Caesar is declared a traitor.

466
00:34:48,421 --> 00:34:50,820
他就不得不反对我了
Then he has no choice but to oppose me openly,

467
00:34:50,850 --> 00:34:54,229
然后就是战争，马克·安东尼不可以收到任何伤害
which means civil war. Antony must not be harmed!

468
00:34:54,279 --> 00:34:56,569
好消息
Dominus, good news.

469
00:34:56,609 --> 00:34:59,678
议会明天复会
The Senate will reconvene tomorrow.

470
00:34:59,718 --> 00:35:01,818
和上次一样
Formally, it is the same session,

471
00:35:01,878 --> 00:35:04,927
所以你明天还可以否决
so you may yet exercise your veto on the motion.

472
00:35:04,977 --> 00:35:07,896
除非庞贝要阻止我
Hmm. Unless Pompey tries to stop me.

473
00:35:07,926 --> 00:35:11,076
很可能
True, he may very well try.

474
00:35:11,405 --> 00:35:13,875
把人们叫齐
Rally the men together.

475
00:35:14,535 --> 00:35:16,364
乌瑞纳斯
vorenus...

476
00:35:16,544 --> 00:35:18,824
所有的人
all of them.

477
00:35:19,633 --> 00:35:22,333
捉迷藏
& Run and hide&

478
00:35:22,643 --> 00:35:25,092
捉迷藏
& Run and hide&

479
00:35:25,622 --> 00:35:28,781
第十三个来了
&The 13th arecoming&

480
00:35:28,851 --> 00:35:32,870
你的人都死了！
& And your men are all dead! &

481
00:35:33,140 --> 00:35:35,330
我多加了些肉豆
I put extra nutmeg in, as you like it.

482
00:35:35,380 --> 00:35:37,889
嫁给我吧，女神
Oh, marry me, goddess.

483
00:35:37,939 --> 00:35:41,058
像你这样的肥猪？
What, a porcine object like you?

484
00:35:41,098 --> 00:35:44,338
谢天谢地，我已经够惨了
Besides, I am already wed, thanks be to evil spirits.

485
00:35:44,378 --> 00:35:47,657
你错了，他是个好人
You are wrong, friend-wife. He is a good man, your man.

486
00:35:47,747 --> 00:35:49,566
好人？
A good man you say?

487
00:35:49,616 --> 00:35:51,456
这些年来，我每晚都在祈祷
For years and years, I'd lie awake at night

488
00:35:51,496 --> 00:35:54,075
让神把他送回来
and beg all the Gods to send him home.

489
00:35:54,125 --> 00:35:57,185
我听到这场那场战役
I'd hear of this battle or that battle and...

490
00:35:57,485 --> 00:35:59,244
我能清清楚楚地看到他
I'd see him, clear as a glass,

491
00:35:59,284 --> 00:36:02,513
满身血污的躺在地上
Iying dead and bloody in the mud somewhere.

492
00:36:05,113 --> 00:36:06,812
我很孤独
I was lonely.

493
00:36:06,872 --> 00:36:08,962
很孤独
I was so lonely.

494
00:36:09,022 --> 00:36:11,031
八年来我一直哭泣
For eight years I wept.

495
00:36:11,071 --> 00:36:15,670
每天孩子们都问，爸爸什么时候回家？
Every day, the girls asking, "When is Papa coming home?

496
00:36:15,720 --> 00:36:18,580
今天吗？
Is it today? When?"

497
00:36:19,839 --> 00:36:22,399
现在他回来了，我却希望他还在高卢
And now he's home, and I wish he was in Gaul.

498
00:36:22,469 --> 00:36:24,178
他真无情无义
He's a cold, mean brute.

499
00:36:24,218 --> 00:36:27,008
对我们连一句亲切的话都不说
Not one loving word to me or his daughters,

500
00:36:27,038 --> 00:36:28,147
一次都没有
not once since he has been home.

501
00:36:28,197 --> 00:36:31,677
他不会哄女人
He is no skilled hand with the women.

502
00:36:31,747 --> 00:36:35,346
不过这些年我跟着他，他一个女人也没动过
But in all these years I fought with him, he never took a woman.

503
00:36:35,386 --> 00:36:38,195
波罗，他对我说：“我的老朋友
"Pullo," he'd say to me, "Pullo, my old friend,

504
00:36:38,235 --> 00:36:40,385
我有个妻子叫内奥比
I have a wife back home, Niobe is her name

505
00:36:40,415 --> 00:36:44,124
她比所有高卢的女人都珍贵”
and she's worth more to me than all the women of Gaul."

506
00:36:44,694 --> 00:36:49,003
谢谢你的好心话，但我知道你在说谎
I thank you for your kind words, but I know you lie.

507
00:36:50,142 --> 00:36:52,522
他不是你的朋友，他告诉我了
He's no friend of yours. He told me so.

508
00:36:52,572 --> 00:36:55,421
他脾气不好
Why, he has a- an ill temper, him.

509
00:36:55,461 --> 00:36:57,291
什么都说
He'd say anything.

510
00:37:00,370 --> 00:37:01,780
安东尼需要所有人
Antony needs every man.

511
00:37:01,820 --> 00:37:04,869
如果你能走，去阿提娅集合
If you can walk, we rendezvous at the house of Atia.

512
00:37:12,037 --> 00:37:13,537
就这么多了
This is all I have left.

513
00:37:13,567 --> 00:37:16,316
卖掉奴隶后还会有些
There will be more when I sell the slaves.

514
00:37:16,366 --> 00:37:20,475
让孩子们回家，呆在家中知道你认为安全了
Get the girls indoors and stay indoors until you know it's safe.

515
00:37:27,104 --> 00:37:29,773
你不高兴让我很伤心
It saddens me that you are unhappy,

516
00:37:29,823 --> 00:37:32,602
因为我很爱你
because I have a deep affection for you.

517
00:37:33,682 --> 00:37:36,211
我回来后再说吧
When I return, we will talk.

518
00:37:48,978 --> 00:37:52,048
这是件喜事
Well, this is a merry do.

519
00:37:53,877 --> 00:37:57,027
奥克塔维娅，你又有精神了
Octavia, my honey, look alive at least.

520
00:37:57,077 --> 00:38:00,496
可怜的安东尼一定认为自己被忘记了
Poor Antony must think himself dead and swimming in Lethe water.

521
00:38:00,536 --> 00:38:04,735
跟这个可怜的家伙讲讲话
Talk to the poor man, ask him questions.

522
00:38:04,815 --> 00:38:07,324
别人还以为你被德国人养大
One would think she'd been raised by Germans.

523
00:38:07,364 --> 00:38:11,773
安东尼，我妈妈的尖叫让你烦吗？
General Antony, does my mother's screaming irritate you?

524
00:38:12,193 --> 00:38:13,302
 你说什么？
Excuse me?

525
00:38:13,357 --> 00:38:15,717
 当你们性交的时候
When you and my mother are in coitus,

526
00:38:15,752 --> 00:38:17,402
尖叫声不断
there is a deal of screaming.

527
00:38:17,452 --> 00:38:20,401
我觉得很烦
I find it extremely irritating.

528
00:38:20,441 --> 00:38:23,110
我向你会不会也这样认为呢？
I wondered whether you did also.

529
00:38:23,160 --> 00:38:24,620
也许你很喜欢？
Or perhaps you like it?

530
00:38:24,680 --> 00:38:26,620
证明你的本领
A testament to your skills.

531
00:38:26,640 --> 00:38:29,259
真可恶
So spiteful, and for what?

532
00:38:29,309 --> 00:38:30,749
你自己侮辱自己
You shame only yourself.

533
00:38:55,633 --> 00:38:59,122
正让她说中了
She has you exact.

534
00:39:00,392 --> 00:39:01,881
让他们见识我们的力量
We show our strength.

535
00:39:01,921 --> 00:39:03,821
告诉他们这儿谁说了算
We show them who owns the Forum,

536
00:39:03,871 --> 00:39:05,780
但不要碰他们
but we do not touch them.

537
00:39:05,780 --> 00:39:07,870
不可以碰安东尼
Antony must not be touched!

538
00:39:07,870 --> 00:39:09,550
 把他们全杀了  不行
 Kill them all, I say.  None of that!

539
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:11,719
庞贝的命令
Pompey's strict orders.

540
00:39:11,759 --> 00:39:15,408
谁找麻烦就会被钉死
Him who starts trouble will be on a cross at nightfall.

541
00:39:15,438 --> 00:39:18,338
不要流血！
So no blood!

542
00:39:25,176 --> 00:39:28,115
让路！我说让开路！
Make a lane there! Make a lane there, I said!

543
00:39:28,145 --> 00:39:31,045
快点！
Come on, you bastards!

544
00:39:58,058 --> 00:40:00,138
跟我来
Rally to me.

545
00:40:00,198 --> 00:40:02,157
跟我来
Rally to me.

546
00:40:02,207 --> 00:40:04,597
跟我来
Rally to me!

547
00:40:13,445 --> 00:40:15,114
不要伤人！
No blood!

548
00:40:32,610 --> 00:40:35,429
你有你想要的了，卡托
You have what you wanted, Cato.

549
00:40:35,469 --> 00:40:38,149
凯撒没选择了
Caesar has no choice now.

550
00:40:38,209 --> 00:40:40,628
明年春天，他会翻过阿尔贝斯
Come the spring, he will cross the Alps

551
00:40:40,658 --> 00:40:44,887
带大军向罗马进发
with his legions and march on Rome.

552
00:40:53,915 --> 00:40:57,054
五个死了
Five dead: three from flux, two from fighting.

553
00:40:57,104 --> 00:41:00,793
十个受伤，八个跑了
10 under medics. Eight absent, believed fled.

554
00:41:00,853 --> 00:41:04,133
战斗力量：236人
 Sir.  Fighting strength: 236 head.

555
00:41:04,183 --> 00:41:06,962
第七队步兵
Seventh Cohort. 12 dead:

556
00:41:07,002 --> 00:41:09,182
12死
six of flux, six of fighting.

557
00:41:09,252 --> 00:41:10,971
三人受伤
Three on the medics.

558
00:41:11,031 --> 00:41:12,831
三人逃跑
Three absent, believed fled.

559
00:41:12,871 --> 00:41:15,170
战斗力量：242人
Fighting strength: 242.

560
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:19,029
马克·安东尼在你后面多远？
Soldier, how far behind you is Mark Antony?

561
00:41:19,059 --> 00:41:21,569
不到一小时
No more than an hour, sir.

562
00:41:25,238 --> 00:41:28,287
 集合！  是，长官！
 Sound assembly!  Sir!

563
00:41:28,757 --> 00:41:30,577
以议会的名义
By order of the Senate,

564
00:41:30,626 --> 00:41:32,916
盖乌斯·优利乌斯·恺撒
Gaius Julius Caesar

565
00:41:32,966 --> 00:41:35,885
成为罗马公敌
is declared an enemy of Rome.

566
00:41:35,935 --> 00:41:37,345
所有公民
All good citizens are bound

567
00:41:37,395 --> 00:41:40,904
有义务去杀掉他
to do him harm if they are able.

568
00:41:59,220 --> 00:42:00,679
我来
I've got him.

569
00:42:02,399 --> 00:42:07,718
这么多年后，庞贝让我吃惊
After all these years, Pompey surprises me.

570
00:42:08,558 --> 00:42:11,147
我曾想主动进攻
I had hoped to provoke some kind of aggression, sure,

571
00:42:11,187 --> 00:42:14,516
但试图在议会谋杀
but to try and kill a Tribune?

572
00:42:14,566 --> 00:42:16,636
护民官？
In the Forum?

573
00:42:17,056 --> 00:42:20,245
The man's found some hard black iron in his soul.

574
00:42:20,285 --> 00:42:24,234
我确定是你那精神错乱的卡托让他做的
I'm sure it was yon demented little worm Cato who put him up to it.

575
00:42:24,584 --> 00:42:27,093
很好，对吗？
It's excellent, this.

576
00:42:27,263 --> 00:42:28,573
接下来？
So, what next?

577
00:42:28,633 --> 00:42:31,712
我们看他还要说什么
Let's see what the men have to say.

578
00:42:33,362 --> 00:42:35,341
别！
Oh, don't do that!

579
00:42:36,721 --> 00:42:39,670
你看上去很好
You look just right as you are.

580
00:42:39,730 --> 00:42:43,559
就像塞莫波莱的里昂纳达
Like Leonidas at Thermopylae.

581
00:42:44,509 --> 00:42:46,599
注意！
Attention!

582
00:42:50,448 --> 00:42:53,037
有什么我可以提到的吗？
Any of your people I can mention?

583
00:42:54,357 --> 00:42:55,936
泰特斯·波罗
Titus Pullo.

584
00:42:55,986 --> 00:42:59,216
砍掉第一个冲向我的人的头
Took the head off the first man that came at me.

585
00:43:04,754 --> 00:43:09,463
士兵们，庞贝和议会
Soldiers, Pompey and the Senate

586
00:43:09,503 --> 00:43:11,813
公开宣布
have formally declared

587
00:43:11,853 --> 00:43:14,872
盖乌斯·优利乌斯·恺撒
that Gaius Julius Caesar

588
00:43:14,912 --> 00:43:17,122
是个公敌
is an enemy of Rome.

589
00:43:17,172 --> 00:43:17,961
不！
No!

590
00:43:18,001 --> 00:43:21,231
他们说我是战犯
They have declared that I am a criminal.

591
00:43:22,220 --> 00:43:24,130
他们公布了，实际上
They have declared, in effect,

592
00:43:24,170 --> 00:43:27,319
你们都是战犯！
that all of you also are criminals!

593
00:43:27,369 --> 00:43:29,549
不！
No!

594
00:43:29,589 --> 00:43:32,658
护民官的否决权无效
The Tribune's veto was not exercised.

595
00:43:32,698 --> 00:43:35,007
护民官马克·安东尼
Peoples Tribune Mark Antony

596
00:43:35,047 --> 00:43:37,307
和13队的50人
and 50 men of the 13th

597
00:43:37,347 --> 00:43:41,386
被1,000庞贝的杂种攻击
were assaulted by 1,000 head of Pompeian scum.

598
00:43:41,436 --> 00:43:43,505
不！
No!

599
00:43:46,225 --> 00:43:50,034
人民的护民官
A Tribune of the plebs

600
00:43:50,084 --> 00:43:52,603
居然在议会门前
assaulted on the steps

601
00:43:52,653 --> 00:43:54,543
被攻击！
of the Senate House!

602
00:43:54,613 --> 00:43:57,072
你们还能想到更严重的亵渎神灵吗？
Can you imagine a more terrible sacrilege?

603
00:43:57,112 --> 00:44:00,921
我们亲爱的共和国正被疯子操纵着
Our beloved Republic is in the hands of madmen.

604
00:44:00,961 --> 00:44:03,081
现在是黑暗时期
This is a dark day,

605
00:44:03,141 --> 00:44:05,580
我站在路中央
and I stand at a fork in the road.

606
00:44:05,640 --> 00:44:08,429
我可以向议会投降
I can abide the law and surrender my arms to the Senate

607
00:44:08,489 --> 00:44:10,219
眼睁睁的看着共和国灭亡
and watch the Republic fall

608
00:44:10,259 --> 00:44:12,059
在暴政和混乱中！
to tyranny and chaos!

609
00:44:12,099 --> 00:44:14,278
或者，我回罗马
Or, I can go home

610
00:44:14,328 --> 00:44:16,588
我可以带着刀剑回去
with my sword in my hand

611
00:44:16,648 --> 00:44:18,627
把那些疯子
and run those maniacs

612
00:44:18,667 --> 00:44:20,697
全都处死！
to the Tarpeian Rock!

613
00:44:20,791 --> 00:44:23,521
Yeah! Yeah!

614
00:44:29,774 --> 00:44:33,554
兵团士兵泰特斯·波罗，请出列！
Legionary Titus Pullo, step forward!

615
00:44:37,933 --> 00:44:40,592
泰特斯·波罗！
Titus Pullo!

616
00:44:45,771 --> 00:44:48,320
当50个勇敢的战士
When 50 brave men of the 13th

617
00:44:48,360 --> 00:44:50,590
与庞贝的1,000人厮杀
fought Pompey's 1,000 in the Forum

618
00:44:50,630 --> 00:44:52,719
试图救护民官时，
and saved the Tribune,

619
00:44:52,769 --> 00:44:57,068
泰特斯·波罗的刀尝到的第一滴血！
it was Legionary Titus Pullo who drew first blood!

620
00:44:57,468 --> 00:45:00,937
500便士！
Here is 500 denarii!

621
00:45:02,737 --> 00:45:04,136
非常感谢
very grateful, sir.

622
00:45:04,186 --> 00:45:06,636
跟我一起吗，泰特斯·波罗？
Are you with me, Titus Pullo?

623
00:45:06,686 --> 00:45:08,895
跟我一起回罗马吗？
 Will you come with me to Rome?  Yes.

624
00:45:08,945 --> 00:45:11,835
是的长官！当然！
Yes, sir! Certainly!

625
00:45:11,885 --> 00:45:14,964
泰特斯·波罗跟着我！
Titus Pullo is with me!

626
00:45:15,034 --> 00:45:17,313
你们呢？你们跟着我吗？
And you? Are you with me?!

627
00:45:17,353 --> 00:45:22,942
是的！
Yeah! Yeah!

628
00:46:14,500 --> 00:46:16,260
你醒了
Ah, you're awake.

629
00:46:16,300 --> 00:46:17,979
水？
Water?

630
00:46:19,429 --> 00:46:20,569
我们换地方
We're moving.

631
00:46:20,944 --> 00:46:22,605
Mmm.

632
00:46:23,828 --> 00:46:27,157
听起来向整个军团，哪里？
The whole legion, sounds like. Where to?

633
00:46:27,607 --> 00:46:29,067
一条河
It's a river.

634
00:46:29,126 --> 00:46:30,866
什么河？
What river?

635
00:46:33,885 --> 00:46:36,445
卢比肯河，冷静
 This is the Rubicon.  Stay calm.

636
00:46:36,505 --> 00:46:38,854
这是叛国
This is rebellion and treason,

637
00:46:38,894 --> 00:46:40,154
我不是叛国者！
and I am no traitor!

638
00:46:40,194 --> 00:46:42,253
太晚了，我们已经在意大利了
It's too late now. We're across. We're in ltaly.

639
00:46:42,293 --> 00:46:44,403
不管怎样，你已经是造反者了
You're a rebel whether you like it or not.

640
00:46:44,453 --> 00:46:46,962
凯撒，你都作了些什么？
Caesar. Caesar, what have you done?

641
00:46:47,002 --> 00:46:48,502
他没选择
He had no choice, had he?

642
00:46:48,542 --> 00:46:50,641
庞贝要杀马克·安东尼
Pompey did try to kill Mark Antony after all.

643
00:46:50,671 --> 00:46:52,741
你们没资格说
You of all men should not dare make that argument.

644
00:46:52,771 --> 00:46:56,970
什么？ 你知道谁被攻击
 How's that?  You know who was being attacked.

645
00:46:57,080 --> 00:46:59,629
什么意思？
I don't know what you mean.

646
00:47:01,059 --> 00:47:02,139
现在没关系了
It doesn't matter now.

647
00:47:02,169 --> 00:47:03,978
我们都死了
We are all dead men any way.

648
00:47:04,018 --> 00:47:07,577
这星期内我们就会被定在十字架上
We'll be hanging from crosses in the Appian Way before the week's out.

649
00:47:07,607 --> 00:47:08,707
不会有事的
We'll be all right.

650
00:47:08,747 --> 00:47:11,007
喝点水，最好渴死
 Have some more water.  Better to die of thirst.

651
00:47:11,037 --> 00:47:14,516
别傻了，喝吧！
Don't be foolish. Drink.

652
00:47:17,835 --> 00:47:21,494
凯撒在意大利！
Caesar is in ltaly!

653
00:47:22,844 --> 00:47:23,634
什么

654
00:47:23,934 --> 00:47:24,563
不可能
Caesar is in ltaly!

655
00:47:24,563 --> 00:47:28,713
凯撒在意大利！

656
00:47:30,682 --> 00:47:33,781
听到了吗？ 听到了
 Have you heard?  I heard.

657
00:47:52,927 --> 00:47:54,247
会发生什么？
What's going to happen?

658
00:47:54,297 --> 00:47:56,986
战争
War is going to happen.

659
00:48:02,924 --> 00:48:05,824
小猪仔，看谁更馋
Who's my greedy little piglet?

660
00:00:03,548 --> 00:00:06,548
翻译:TLF字幕组

